## 2. Problem → Solution Matrix

Based on RFQ pain points, here's how the demo addresses each:

| # | Client Pain Point (RFQ) | Demo Solution | Screen/Component |
|---|------------------------|---------------|------------------|
| 1 | No dedicated mileage management tools | Purpose-built mileage dashboard with real-time tracking | Dashboard + KPI Cards |
| 2 | IBM Maximo only does asset management | Integrated mileage + maintenance planning | Planning View |
| 3 | Manual Excel management | Interactive visual timeline with drag operations | Planning View (Timeline) |
| 4 | Folder-driven data storage | Centralized visualization of all fleet data | Sidebar + Data Grid |
| 5 | Limited maintenance-operations integration | Single pane of glass for both teams | Unified Planning View |
| 6 | Non-compliance risk (underrun/overrun) | Visual alerts + compliance indicators | Alert Banners + Color coding |
| 7 | No predictive simulations | **Sandbox Mode** for what-if scenarios | Sandbox Mode (Primary Feature) |
| 8 | Insufficient resource visibility | Resource utilization panels | Resource Panel + Heatmap |
| 9 | Manual handling delays | Automated scheduling visualization | Timeline + Conflict Detection |

