## 6. Sandbox Mode (What-If Scenarios) - PRIMARY FEATURE

### 6.1 Concept

Sandbox Mode provides a **simulation environment** where users can experiment with schedule changes without affecting the production baseline. This directly addresses RFQ requirement #7: "Availability to perform simulations on various planning and scheduling options."

### 6.2 Mode Toggle UI

