## 7. Components Specification

### 7.1 Task Block Component

```typescript
interface TaskBlockProps {
  id: string;
  trainId: string;
  startDay: number;
  duration: number;
  type: 'A-Check' | 'B-Check' | 'C-Check' | 'D-Overhaul';
  status: 'scheduled' | 'in-progress' | 'completed';
  hasConflict: boolean;
  isModified: boolean;  // Sandbox mode - shows violet outline
  manHours: number;
  track: number;
}
```

**Visual States:**
- Default: Solid color based on type
- Hover: Brightness +20%
- Selected: Cyan border (2px)
- Conflict: Red pulsing border
- Modified (Sandbox): Violet dashed border

