## 9. Interactions & Gestures

### 9.1 Canvas Navigation

| Gesture | Action | API |
|---------|--------|-----|
| Drag | Pan canvas | OrthographicController |
| Scroll | Zoom (centered on cursor) | onViewStateChange |
| Pinch (touch) | Zoom | @use-gesture/react |
| Double-click | Zoom in to point | Animated transition |
| Double-tap (touch) | Zoom in to point | Animated transition |

### 9.2 Task Interactions

| Interaction | Live Mode | Sandbox Mode |
|-------------|-----------|--------------|
| Hover | Show tooltip | Show tooltip + edit handles |
| Click | Select (show details) | Select (show details) |
| Drag | - | Move task (reschedule) |
| Drag edges | - | Resize duration |
| Right-click | Context menu (view) | Context menu (edit) |

### 9.3 Keyboard Shortcuts

| Key | Action |
|-----|--------|
| `+` / `=` | Zoom in |
| `-` | Zoom out |
| `0` | Reset zoom to 1x |
| `Arrow keys` | Pan canvas |
| `Escape` | Clear selection |
| `Delete` | Delete task (Sandbox) |
| `Ctrl+Z` | Undo (Sandbox) |
| `Ctrl+Y` | Redo (Sandbox) |
| `S` | Toggle Sandbox mode |

